# AXIUM_EXPERIMENTS Changelog

## 2025-12-03 - AxObjectClass v0.1: Fase 0+1+2 Complete (9/39 shapes)

### Summary
Completed foundation, pilot, and all 9 primitives conversion to AxObjectClass v0.1 standard.
This establishes the MODEL PATTERN for all PROCEDURAL/GENERATIVE SDF shapes.

---

## 2025-12-03 - AxObjectClass v0.1 Fase 2: Primitives Conversion (8 shapes)

### Converted - All Primitives to AxObjectClass v0.1
- **obj/primitives/Capsule.hx** - Line segment with spherical caps
- **obj/primitives/Cone.hx** - Circular cone primitive
- **obj/primitives/Cylinder.hx** - Circular cylinder primitive
- **obj/primitives/Ellipsoid.hx** - Stretched sphere primitive
- **obj/primitives/Plane.hx** - Infinite plane primitive
- **obj/primitives/Pyramid.hx** - Square pyramid primitive
- **obj/primitives/Sphere.hx** - Perfect sphere primitive
- **obj/primitives/Torus.hx** - Donut-shaped primitive

All follow Box reference implementation:
- Implements `AxObjectClass` interface
- `new()` constructor for instance-based pattern
- `shader()` method returning shader instance
- `object()` method returning PdfObject metadata
- Shader classes unchanged (extend BaseRaymarchShader)

### Testing - Fase 2 Validation
- ✅ All 9 primitives compile successfully
- ✅ All 9 primitives render correctly (--sc --box --capsule --cone --cylinder --ellipsoid --plane --pyramid --sphere --torus)
- ✅ Visual verification: all shapes display identically to before conversion
- ✅ ShapeCatalog hybrid system works seamlessly (9 AxObjectClass + 30 legacy)

### Progress
- **Converted**: 9/39 shapes (23%)
  - ✅ Primitives: 9/9 (Box, Capsule, Cone, Cylinder, Ellipsoid, Plane, Pyramid, Sphere, Torus)
- **Remaining**: 30/39 shapes (77%)
  - 2D Primitives: 5 shapes
  - Derivates: 6 shapes
  - 2D Organics: 7 shapes
  - 3D Organic: 12 shapes

---

## 2025-12-03 - AxObjectClass v0.1 Fase 0+1: Foundation + Box Pilot

### Added - AxObjectClass Standard
- **AxObjectClass.hx interface** - Formal contract for all PROCEDURAL/GENERATIVE SDF shapes
  - `shader():hxsl.Shader` - Returns GPU raymarching shader
  - `object():PdfObject` - Returns procedural shape metadata for serialization/generation
  - This is the MODEL PATTERN for all future shape implementations

- **PdfObject.hx typedef** - Metadata structure for procedural shape description
  - `name:String` - Human-readable shape identifier
  - `sdf:{kind:String, params:Dynamic}` - SDF function metadata (sdBox, sdSphere, etc.)
  - `transform:{position, rotation, scale}` - Spatial transformation data
  - `material:{color, roughness, metallic}` - Visual properties
  - Enables JSON export, procedural generation, and shape serialization

### Changed - Box Pilot Conversion
- **obj/primitives/Box.hx** - Converted to AxObjectClass v0.1 standard
  - Removed static `color` and `distance()` methods (old pattern)
  - Implements `AxObjectClass` interface
  - Added `new()` constructor for instance-based pattern
  - Added `shader()` method returning BoxShader instance
  - Added `object()` method returning PdfObject with Box metadata
  - BoxShader remains unchanged - extends BaseRaymarchShader
  - **This is the reference implementation for all future shapes**

- **ShapeCatalog.hx** - Updated to support AxObjectClass pattern
  - `createShaderForShape()` now tries AxObjectClass pattern first
  - Falls back to legacy pattern for unconverted shapes (38 remaining)
  - Hybrid system allows incremental conversion of shapes
  - Instantiates shape object, calls `shader()` method

### Testing - Fase 0+1 Validation
- ✅ Box compiles successfully with AxObjectClass pattern
- ✅ Box renders identically to before (--sc --box)
- ✅ Screenshot saved to sc/Box.png - visual verification passed
- ✅ ShapeCatalog hybrid system works for both patterns
- ✅ All 39 shapes still load and render (Box via new pattern, 38 via legacy)

### Architecture Decision
- **Shader Strategy: Option B** - Return custom shader per shape (hxsl.Shader)
  - Most flexible approach for PROCEDURAL/GENERATIVE patterns
  - Each shape owns its shader instance
  - Enables future extensions (multi-shader shapes, shader composition, etc.)

### Next Steps
- **Fase 2-6**: Convert remaining 38 shapes to AxObjectClass v0.1
  - Primitives (8 remaining): Capsule, Cone, Cylinder, Ellipsoid, Plane, Pyramid, Sphere, Torus
  - 2D Primitives (5): Box2D, Circle, Heart, RoundedBox2D, Star
  - Derivates (6): HalfCapsule, HoledPlane, HollowBox, HollowSphere, QuarterTorus, ShellCylinder
  - 2D Organics (7): FlowerPetalRing, LeafPair, LeafSpiral, LotusFringe, OrnateKnot, SpiralVine, VineCurl
  - 3D Organic (12): BlobbyCluster, BubbleCrown, BulbTreeCrown, DripCone, JellyDonut, KnotTube, MeltedBox, PuffyCross, RibbonTwist, SoftSphereWrap, UndulatingPlane, WavyCapsule

